{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Let {\i f}\u8196?=\u8196?({\i A}\u8196?\u8594?\u8196?{\i B}) be any function. Prove that the graph {\i \u915?}{\sub {\i f}} of {\i f} is isomorphic to {\i A}.\par}
